ttps://s21.q4cdn.com/399680738/files/doc_financials/2023/q4/META-Q4-2023-Ea=
rnings-Call-Transcript.pdf ) :

I recently shared that by the end of this year we=E2=80=99ll have about 350=
k H100s and including other GPUs that=E2=80=99ll be around 600k H100 equiva=
lents of compute. We=E2=80=99re well-positioned now because of the lessons =
that we learned from Reels. We initially under-built our GPU clusters for R=
eels, and when we were going through that I decided that we should build en=
ough capacity to support both Reels and another Reels-sized AI service that=
 we expected to emerge so we wouldn=E2=80=99t be in that situation again. A=
nd at the time the decision was somewhat controversial and we faced a lot o=
f questions about capex spending, but I=E2=80=99m really glad that we did t=
his.

The part that people forget about Meta=E2=80=99s nadir is that Nvidia hit a=
 nadir at the same time ( https://stratechery.com/2022/nvidia-in-the-valley=
/?access_token=3DeyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6InN0cmF0ZWNoZXJ5LnBhc3Nwb3J0Lm=
